{
  "texts": [
    "Limitations.",
    "Despite these promising results, our approach assumes reliable rendering from 3DGS under constrained trajectory deviations and currently decouples value modeling from policy optimization.",
    "Future work includes extending our current results to diverse driving datasets, exploring the online RL training over the 3DGS simulator, and deploying MPA to the multi-modal foundation models to enhance reasoning capability for more severe distribution shifts in autonomous driving.",
